Bryan Pearce, Ernst & Young's 
Americas Director, discusses what the U.S. government can do to 
help support small businesses.  Pearce talks with Bloomberg's 
Pimm Fox and Courtney Donohoe on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking 
Stock."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:42
 